Source: pg-liquid
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/michael-golfi/pg_liquid

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-liquid
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-liquid
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Liquid-inspired Datalog graph query extension for PostgreSQL
  pg_liquid brings Liquid-style graph querying, assertions, recursive closure,
  and row normalization to PostgreSQL as a native C extension.
